<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; font-size: 13px; color: #222; line-height: 1.7; }
  .letterhead { text-align: center; border-bottom: 3px solid #361963; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .company-name { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: #361963; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .company-address { font-size: 11px; color: #666; }
  .ref-line { font-size: 11px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .subject { font-weight: bold; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 15px; text-decoration: underline; color: #c00; }
  .content p { margin-bottom: 12px; text-align: justify; }
  .signature { margin-top: 60px; }
  .signature-line { border-top: 1px solid #333; width: 200px; margin-top: 50px; }
  .warning-box { background: #fff5f5; border: 1px solid #fcc; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; border-left: 4px solid #c00; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="letterhead">
    <div class="company-name">{{companyLegalName}}</div>
    <div class="company-address">{{companyAddress}}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="ref-line">Date: {{today}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; CONFIDENTIAL</div>

  <p>Dear <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>
  <p>Employee Code: {{employeeCode}}</p>

  <div class="subject">WARNING LETTER</div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>This letter serves as a formal warning regarding the following matter:</p>

    <div class="warning-box">
      <strong>Reason:</strong> {{warningReason}}
    </div>

    {{#if warningDetails}}<p>{{warningDetails}}</p>{{/if}}

    <p>This behavior/action is in violation of company policy and is unacceptable. You are hereby advised to take corrective action immediately.</p>

    <p>Please note that any recurrence of such behavior may lead to further disciplinary action, up to and including termination of employment.</p>

    <p>We expect your full cooperation in ensuring that this matter is resolved promptly.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="signature">
    <p>For <strong>{{companyLegalName}}</strong></p>
    <div class="signature-line"></div>
    <p>Authorized Signatory</p>
  </div>

  <div style="margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px dashed #ccc; padding-top: 20px;">
    <p><strong>Employee Acknowledgement:</strong></p>
    <p>I acknowledge receipt of this warning letter.</p>
    <br/><br/>
    <p>Signature: ____________________ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Date: ____________________</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
